  -files/terminatorx-3.80.fixGnomeMakefile.patch, terminatorx-3.81.ebuild,
  terminatorx-3.82.ebuild:
  Dont make use of the deprecated oggvorbis useflag any longer, see #94254.
  Marked 3.82 stable on amd64 and x86. Removed unnecessary patches.

*terminatorx-3.82 (20 Feb 2005)

